**Summary of what was built:**
- **`useCopyTasks` hook** — shared clipboard logic that copies single task title as plain text, or multiple as a bulleted markdown list
- **Cmd+C keyboard shortcut** in TaskListView and MyDayView — only fires when tasks are selected and no text input is focused; works in both list and kanban views
- **"Copy" menu item** in single-task ContextMenu (Clipboard icon, after Duplicate, before Delete)
- **"Copy" menu item** in BulkContextMenu (Clipboard icon, after Snooze, before Delete)
- **Toast feedback**: "Copied" for single task, "Copied N tasks" for multiple
